content: Just got the ethical framework for Xander plugged into a major bank's trading system. Now we're under the microscope for real. Every move matters now. We're preparing for the demo, and the stakes are high.

Xander just made his first ethical trade on his own and it went well! It's cool, but the real test is how he'll deal with the market's ups and downs over time. This could be the start of something huge!
